.TH BSTATUS 1 "2026-04-23" "smartmet-monitor" "SmartMet Server"
.SH NAME
bstatus \- HTTP status code distribution from a SmartMet access log
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bstatus
.RI [ LOG-FILE ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bstatus
counts HTTP status codes and prints a distribution table: each code
with its count and percentage plus a horizontal Unicode bar scaled
to the most common code. A second block groups codes by class
(2xx, 3xx, 4xx, 5xx).
.PP
Reads standard input when no log file is given.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR bstat (1),
.BR bchart (1),
.BR burls (1),
.BR bkeys (1),
.BR smtop (1)
